n-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #424242; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9973 lazyloaded lazy-load-active\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; vertical-align: middle; transition: opacity 1s ease 0s; opacity: 1; clear: both; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://bizevent.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/49938600_1013924452127292_1488019848087732224_n-min.jpg\" alt=\"tổ chức lễ khởi c&ocirc;ng động thổ tại h&agrave; nội\" width=\"650\" height=\"461\" data-src=\"https://bizevent.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/49938600_1013924452127292_1488019848087732224_n-min.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://bizevent.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/49938600_1013924452127292_1488019848087732224_n-min.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #424242; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Thi&ecirc;n Thanh nhận tổ chức lễ khởi c&ocirc;ng, động thổ như:</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #424242; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&ndash; C&aacute;c khu dự &aacute;n đ&ocirc; thị, trung t&acirc;m thương mại, cầu đường</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #424242; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">&ndash; Dự &aacute;n x&acirc;y dựng trường học, bệnh viện, nh&agrave; m&aacute;y,&hellip;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #424242; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-9974 lazyloaded lazy-load-active\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; vertical-align: middle; transition: opacity 1s ease 0s; opacity: 1; clear: both; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://bizevent.vn/wp-content/uploads/2020/0